<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">(i) use, reproduce, modify, adapt, translate, distribute, publish, create derivative works from and publicly display any comments, bug reports, or feedback provided by you to the Site (collectively, &ldquo;Customer Feedback&rdquo;) throughout the world in any media for any purpose, now known or hereafter devised; and</p>
