<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">(a) OnlyOPD may, at its sole and absolute discretion, allow cancellations, exchanges or refunds on Product(s) or service purchased which are goods, on a case-by-case basis, on the following conditions:</p>
