<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">(b) Cancellations, exchanges, or refunds on Product(s) which are goods may be subject to a processing fee as shall be determined by OnlyOPD in its sole and absolute discretion, on a case-by-case basis.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">(c) OnlyOPD may, at its sole and absolute discretion, allow extension of the redemption or validity period of a Voucher, on a case-by-case basis, subject to the availability of the Partner, provided the following are fulfilled:</p>
