<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">5.2 Subject to any applicable laws, OnlyOPD reserves the right to impose a fee for access of your Personal Data in the amounts as permitted therein.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">5.3 In respect of your right to access and/or correct your Personal Data, OnlyOPD has the right to refuse your requests to access and/or make any correction to your Personal Data for the reasons permitted under the law, for example where the expenses of providing access to you is disproportionate to the risks to your or another person&rsquo;s privacy.</p>
