<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%;">Our Application may contain links to websites or applications operated and maintained by third-parties, over which we have no control. Privacy policies for these third-party sites and applications may be different from our Privacy Policy. You access these third-party sites and applications at your own risk. You should always read the privacy policy of a linked site or applications before disclosing any personal information on such site and/or through such applications. OnlyOPD is not responsible for information you submit to third-parties.</p>
